</div><div class='clearall'></div></li>
<li><div class="step_num">2</div><b class='whb'>Pick a stall</b>. Usually the first stall when you walk in is the cleanest. If the first one's taken, try to find one that appears reasonably clean. Make sure the door can close completely, and if none of them do, be ready to hold it closed with your feet.<div class='clearall'></div></li>
<li><div class="step_num">3</div><b class='whb'>Prepare your seat</b>. Wipe the seat with fresh toilet paper, whether it was dirty or not. Use a seat cover if one is provided. If the bathroom has no seat covers fold toilet paper over where you will be sitting to create one. You can also lay toilet paper inside the bowl on the surface of the water to prevent the water from splashing if it bothers you.<div class='clearall'></div></li>
<li><div class="step_num">4</div><b class='whb'>However, if you're a woman and going for #1</b>: Position your butt somewhat about six inches over the seat and go. If hovering and holding balance is difficult for you, hold onto such as a handle or the toilet paper dispenser and/or enlarge the gap between your butt and the toilet.<div class='clearall'></div></li>
<li><div class="step_num">5</div><b class='whb'>Clean up</b>. After wiping, get up and throw your make-shift seat cover into the bowl. Zip up and flush. Use your hand to flush, you will have a chance to wash them before you leave the bathroom.<div class='clearall'></div></li>
<li><div class="step_num">6</div><b class='whb'>Roll out some paper towels before washing your hands</b>. This way you don't have to touch the dispenser after washing hands.<div class='clearall'></div></li>
<li><div class="step_num">7</div><a href="/Wash-Your-Hands" title="Wash Your Hands"><b class='whb'>Wash your hands</a> and always use soap</b>. Dry your hands with the paper towel.<div class='clearall'></div></li>
<li><div class="step_num">8</div><b class='whb'>Use paper towel to turn off water if applicable</b>.<div class='clearall'></div></li>
<li class="steps_li final_li"><div class="step_num">9</div><b class='whb'>Either push the door open with your foot or if you need to, use paper towel to open door if you need to grab the handle to get out</b>.<div class='clearall'></div><div class='wh_ad'><script type="text/javascript"><!--

